com.iver.cit.gvsig.geoprocess.core
Interface IGeoprocessController

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractGeoprocessController, BufferGeoprocessController, ClipGeoprocessController, ConvexHullGeoprocessController, DifferenceGeoprocessController, DissolveGeoprocessController, IntersectionGeoprocessController, LineCleanGeoprocessController, MergeGeoprocessController, PolygonBuildGeoprocessController, ReprojectGeoprocessController, SpatialJoinGeoprocessController, UnionGeoprocessController, XYShiftGeoprocessController
public interface IGeoprocessController

This interface receives user inputs from a GeoprocessPanel (GUI component associated to a geoprocess) and prepare the execution of the geoprocess.
In a model-view-controller architecture, IGeoprocessController would be the Controller, IGeoprocessPanel the view, and IGeoprocess the model.

Author:
azabala TODO Maybe we could add an intermediate interface, IUserEntry, to allow to work with GUI environments like this (IGeoprocessPanel) and with shell environments.
